flowchart TD
    A[User Request] --> B[Agent.prompt(messages)]
    B --> C{Outer Loop}
    C --> D[Inner Loop: Turn]
    D --> E[Inject pending<br/>(steering/follow-up)?]
    E --> F[Stream Assistant<br/>via streamFn]
    F --> G{Has tool calls?}
    G -->|Yes| H[Execute Tools<br/>Sequential]
    H --> I{After each tool:<br/>Steering queued?}
    I -->|Yes| J[Set steeringAfterTools<br/>Skip remaining]
    I -->|No| K[Continue next tool]
    J --> L
    K --> H
    H -->|All done| L[Push ToolResults<br/>Emit events]
    L --> M[Emit turn_end]
    M --> N{Check steering<br/>(getSteeringMessages)}
    N -->|Steering| O[pendingMessages = steering<br/>Continue inner]
    N -->|No| P{Outer: getFollowUpMessages}
    P -->|Follow-up| Q[pending = follow-up<br/>Repeat outer]
    P -->|None| R[Emit agent_end<br/>Return]
    O --> D
    Q --> D

    style C fill:#e1f5e1
    style D fill:#f5e1e1
    style H fill:#e1f5e1